      "id": "3",
      "question": "The ratio of two numbers is 3:4 and their LCM is 180. Find the smaller number.",
      "options": [
        "45",
        "48",
        "54",
        "60"
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "45",
      "explanation": "3k×4k / gcd = 180. k=5. Numbers = 15 and 20... wait: LCM(3k,4k)=12k. 12k=180, k=15. Smaller=3×15=45."
    },
