      "options": [
        "1",
        "2",
        "3",
        "4"
      ],
      "correctAnswer": "3",
      "explanation": "Adding 3: 8, 14, 22, 40. 8:14=4:7 and 22:40=11:20. Not equal...let k: (5+k)(37+k)=(11+k)(19+k). k=1."
